high_descs: Turn right and head down the passage on the left and head to the desk in the bedroom.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn right and head down the passage on the left and reach the pan at the end and reach the bed.
Put the knife on the pan.
Pick up the pan from the bed.
Turn right and head to the kitchen on the right and reach the countertop next to the microwave.
Put the pan on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Put the Knife on the Pan on the CounterTop.

high_descs: Turn right then left, and then walk down the hallway; at the end of hallway, turn left to enter the room, then turn right to walk into the space between the desk and bed; turn right to face the desk.
Pick up the knife on the desk that is between the box and pot.
Turn around to exit pan; then turn right to walk down the hallway and go into the pan across you while passing by the pan; keep walking till the pan ahead, then turn right to face the pan.
Put the knife on the fry pan on the bed.
Pick up the stack of pan and knife.
Turn right to exit room; walk ahead and turn right after passing the countertop, then turn right at the refrigerator to get into the corner of the microwave.
Put the stack of pan and knife on the countertop, on the right of microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a Knife over a Pan and bring them to CounterTop.

high_descs: Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the desk on your right
Pick up knife from the desk
Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the pan on your right
Place knife on the pan
Pick up pan from the bed
Turn right and head straight, turn right and proceed walk into the room and head straight, turn right towards the counter top
Place pan on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Obtaining pan from various locations and arranging them in a counter top
